Tortoises are pictured at the Shahjalal International Airport in Dhaka on April 17, 2012. Bangladesh customs authorities seized more than 400 tortoises at the country's main airport as the reptiles were being smuggled from India to Thailand, an official said. Visit  www.bloomberg.com/sustainability   for the latest from Bloomberg News about energy, natural resources and global business.